author: Muhammad Zulhusni
description:
Oracle has released Java 25 (Oracle JDK 25), the newest version of the language and platform that has been around for over three decades. The update brings thousands of improvements, many aimed at boosting developer productivity and strengthening performance, stability, and security. Oracle will provide long-term support for at least eight years, with quarterly updates […]

title: Oracle releases Java 25 with focus on developers and AI
